Sure, here are some examples:

1. *Glasno* pevaj dok ti srce bije. (Sing loudly while your heart beats.) 
2. Molim te, ne govori tako *glasno*. (Please don't speak so loudly.)
3. Ulica je bila *glasna* od automobila. (The street was noisy from the cars.)
4. Deca su se igrala *glasno* u parku. (The children were playing loudly in the park.)
5. Ona je *glasno* smejala na šali. (She laughed loudly at the joke.)
6. *Glasnoća* muzike je bila prejaka. (The loudness of the music was too strong.)
7. Glumci su govorili *glasno* da ih čuje cela publika. (The actors spoke loudly so that the whole audience could hear them.)
8. Čuo sam *glasan* zvuk iz motora. (I heard a loud sound from the engine.)

I hope these examples are helpful!